snippet.title: Has It Finally Been Revealed Who From The Royal Family Asked About Archie's Skin Tone?
snippet.description:
One of the biggest bombshell reveals in Meghan Markle and Prince Harry's interview with Oprah in March 2021 had to do with the claim that an unnamed senior royal had raised questions about the potential skin color of Harry and Meghan's child.

At the time, Meghan and Harry resolved not to share who had raised the issue of their son Archie's potential complexion, but a new book claims to have the answer — and it's allegedly one of the most senior royals. Has it finally been revealed who from the royal family asked about Archie's skin tone?

#PrinceHarry #MeghanMarkle #RoyalFamily
